I [[Burundi]] abana batangura amashule yisumbuye bafise imyaka cumi n'ibiri canke cumi n'itatu iyo batahitiye. Mu bisanzwe amashule y'isumbuye agizwe n'ibice bibiri. Mu gice cambere abana bamara imyaka ine kuntebe y'ishure. Ivyirwa bikuru bikuru bakurikira n'ibi:
# Indimi ([[igifaransa]] [[icongereza]] hamwe n' igiswahiri)
# Ibiharuro
# Akahise
# Indonda bihugu
# Uburimyi
# Kunonora imitsi
# Ubuhinga

Kugira babandanye igice c'akabiri, bategerezwa kumenya ikibazo co mu mwaka w'icumi.Abafise ubumenyi bujanye n'ibiharuro, barashobora guhitamwo kubandanya amashule y'isumbuye mu gisata c'ibiharuro n'ibindi vyirwa bijanye.

Abafise amanuta meza mu ndimi n'ibindi vyirwa bijanye nabo,bashobora ku bandanya amashule y'isumbuye mu gisata c'indimi.

Murico gihe, ivyirwa abana biga biba bishimikiye ku ndimi canke kubiharuro.

Bitayeko, abana barashobora  guhitamwo kwiga amashule y'imyuga.

Abana bahisemwo kunonosora ibiharuro canke indimi, bategerezwa gukora ikibazo co mu mwaka w'icumi na gatatu.Ni ikibazo ca leta gihambaye cane gitanga uburenganzira bwo kwinjira muri kaminuza.

